::Orchestra::

       Orchestra smiled at Blacknightmare, then ran off to Zone 5.  Then
suddenly, he stopped, and felt a pain in his back.

       "EEGH!" He yelled, as the pain grew intensely.

    Then, two strange things sprouted out from Orchestra's back.  He didn't
know what they were, they were long tubes, kindof like a thruster you'd see
on a......That was it!  Orchestra had a built-in jetpack unit!

      "Hey, babe, check this out!" He yelled quickly to Blacknightmare
before thrusting up into the air.

       "YEEHAW!" he yelled, flying around in spirals and doing figure-8s in
mid-air.  He then landed.

        "I wish Composer had of told me about this!!! Well, wadda ya say,
need a lift anywhere?" He asked Blacknightmare, turning around so his back
was facing her.
